label: Kame Krew Minting page
caption: Kame Krew Fight Camp
description: Kame Krew Fight Camp is a collection of 420 Kames giving 50% to Wor. Watthana - a rural Muay Thai gym in Isaan, Thailand keeping kids healthy, educated, and safe. The other half of the funds are being reinvested right back to building an online fitness/MMA training platform on Cardano. With your help, we'll give kids a safe home AND onboard coaches and athletes.
